name: WAS Gelata
description:
About Gelata

Gelata actually started off as a request from @FoxDude. Based on a set of jelly fish photos and jelly-esque art. Similar to The Last of Us it comes in a subject-style-hybrid flavor, and a exclusively style based flavor.

Don't hesitate to comment about any questions. And I'd love to see your reviews!

modelVersions.name: Gelata Puella v1
modelVersions.description: Gelata Puella (Jelly Girl) is a mix of a style and subject training. It's used similar to The Last of Us TI and mixed in with a subject, but is sort of flexible in portraits.
